Dadeville peeps...... A family from Fair Play lost everything in the Tornado!!!! I’m reposting from their school page. I will add their clothing sizes in the comments.

PLEASE SHARE—-Jesse and Melanie Chance’s family lost everything in the tornado yesterday afternoon. They are all safe and sound but have nothing left. Money donations may be made at the school starting Monday and the money will be given directly to the family. Checks should be made to the family but if you make it to the school district we will still get the funds to the family. We will also have a fund raiser but we wanted to start the “neighbor helping neighbor” immediately. We plan to post specific sizes for clothing donations as available. Thank you in advance for your assistance and kindness. Every dollar goes directly to the family.

post_text:
ACT prep.....

Prepfactory is a free, interactive ACT test prep site for teachers and students. This site breaks the ACT test into bite-sized concepts and provides strategy tips, practice tests, and a personalized study path so a student can master the test. Go to: www.prepfactory,com to get signed up.
Also students can go to: www.studentact.org and choose "Start Practicing with ACT Academy", select "I am a student", and then set up an account. This site provides videos as well as other study options for the ACT.
